building.description: Alta at K Station is the premiere rental residence located between River North and the West Loop. Inside these two modern towers, you will find stylish eco-friendly rental residences designed for the dynamic lifestyle of the modern urban dweller. Shop, dine, socialize and play in the neighborhood hotspots, all just steps from your front door. Access the LRT at K Station for your commute downtown or walk to the Wacker Business Corridor. Schedule your personal tour!
